\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Scar contracture }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Eccliptic plane}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Material boiled away, denuded of volatile material,}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Falling from the mountain brow}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Thoughts turned through central bank operations, the lonely first era, the currency denomination of trade in the early modern period, the causes of the fall of Rome, Bretton Woods, the fiscal profligacy of LBJ\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s Great Society programs, the creation of the eurodollar, the internal mental states of 70\u8217\'92s Keynesian economists, the origins of money, the operation of foreign exchange markets, the Volcker shock, Newtonian mechanics and gravity wells, derivatives and the rise of modern hedge funds, the causes of the Bolshevik revolution, the origins and motivations of the Federal Reserve, and TARP. }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Into more primitive categories of thought}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 A separate accident, their existence, arbitrary. Inverted by a caprice of power. The true tragedy of tragic choices is that they\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92re unchosen.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Compet impact}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 The battle explodes. Lines of fate tying. The demosn fall upon eachother. The gods lost the root of their power. A hunt which lasted for an age.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
